{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/leetcode-move-zeros","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Leetcode move zeros(Python)","date":"January 3rd, 2020"},"html":"<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/move-zeroes/\">문제 링크</a></p>\n<h4>접근 (의식의 흐름)</h4>\n<p>아래 두 조건이 신경쓰였지만 그냥 <code>filter</code> 함수를 사용하고 기존 길이에서 부족한 만큼 0으로 채우는 방법을 사용하려 했어요. 하지만 역시 filter는 새로운 array를 만들어주기 때문에 문제 조건을 만족시키지 못했어요.</p>\n<p><code>문제조건</code></p>\n<pre><code>1. You must do this in-place without making a copy of the array.\n2. Minimize the total number of operations.\n</code></pre>\n<p>결국 완전 탐색을 하며 0인 경우 삭제하고, 몇 개 삭제했는지 기억해두고 나중에 뒤에 붙여주는 방식으로 문제를 풀었어요.</p>\n<h4>코드</h4>\n<pre><code class=\"language-python\">class Solution:\n    def moveZeroes(self, nums: List[int]) -> None:\n        idx = 0\n        zerocounter = 0\n        while idx &#x3C; len(nums):\n            if nums[idx] == 0:\n                del nums[idx]\n                zerocounter += 1\n                continue\n            idx += 1\n        nums += [0]*zerocounter\n</code></pre>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a1bdcc200bcfcc7ddfd52f8b280f04f7/b77c0/image-20200103114028190.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 19.662058371735792%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image-20200103114028190\"\n        title=\"image-20200103114028190\"\n        src=\"/static/a1bdcc200bcfcc7ddfd52f8b280f04f7/dc2fe/image-20200103114028190.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a1bdcc200bcfcc7ddfd52f8b280f04f7/fc8b9/image-20200103114028190.png 163w,\n/static/a1bdcc200bcfcc7ddfd52f8b280f04f7/d53b1/image-20200103114028190.png 325w,\n/static/a1bdcc200bcfcc7ddfd52f8b280f04f7/dc2fe/image-20200103114028190.png 650w,\n/static/a1bdcc200bcfcc7ddfd52f8b280f04f7/6251f/image-20200103114028190.png 975w,\n/static/a1bdcc200bcfcc7ddfd52f8b280f04f7/72325/image-20200103114028190.png 1300w,\n/static/a1bdcc200bcfcc7ddfd52f8b280f04f7/b77c0/image-20200103114028190.png 1302w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>무난하지만 성능 향상에 대해서 좀 더 공부가 필요한 것 같아요.</p>"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"leetcode-move-zeros"}}}